#. <section id="vagga"><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.130" id="130"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an2.130-140:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:0.2"
msgid "12. Āyācanavagga"
msgstr "12. Aspiration"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:0.3"
msgid "130"
msgstr "130"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc130.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:130.1.1"
msgid "“Saddho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu evaṃ sammā āyācamāno āyāceyya:"
msgstr "“A faithful monk would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:130.1.2"
msgid "‘tādiso homi yādisā sāriputtamoggallānā’ti."
msgstr "‘May I be like Sāriputta and Moggallāna!’"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:130.1.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvakānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ yadidaṃ "
"sāriputtamoggallānā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my monk disciples, that is, Sāriputta "
"and Moggallāna.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.131" id="131"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:130.1.4"
msgid "131"
msgstr "131"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc131.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:131.1.1"
msgid "“Saddhā, bhikkhave, bhikkhunī evaṃ sammā āyācamānā āyāceyya:"
msgstr "“A faithful nun would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:131.1.2"
msgid "‘tādisī homi yādisī khemā ca bhikkhunī uppalavaṇṇā cā’ti."
msgstr "‘May I be like the nuns Khemā and Uppalavaṇṇā!’"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:131.1.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvikānaṃ bhikkhunīnaṃ yadidaṃ khemā "
"ca bhikkhunī uppalavaṇṇā cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my nun disciples, that is, the nuns "
"Khemā and Uppalavaṇṇā.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.132" id="132"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:131.1.4"
msgid "132"
msgstr "132"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc132.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:132.1.1"
msgid "“Saddho, bhikkhave, upāsako evaṃ sammā āyācamāno āyāceyya:"
msgstr "“A faithful layman would rightly aspire:"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:132.1.2"
msgid "‘tādiso homi yādiso citto ca gahapati hatthako ca āḷavako’ti."
msgstr "‘May I be like the householder Citta and Hatthaka of Aḷavī!’"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:132.1.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvakānaṃ upāsakānaṃ yadidaṃ citto ca "
"gahapati hatthako ca āḷavako”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my male lay followers, that is, the "
"householder Citta and Hatthaka of Aḷavī.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.133" id="133"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:132.1.4"
msgid "133"
msgstr "133"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.89"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc133.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:133.1.1"
msgid "“Saddhā, bhikkhave, upāsikā evaṃ sammā āyācamānā āyāceyya:"
msgstr "“A faithful laywoman would rightly aspire:"

#. VAR: veḷukaṇḍakiyā → veḷukaṇṭakiyā (s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an2.130-140:133.1.2"
msgid ""
"‘tādisī homi yādisī khujjuttarā ca upāsikā veḷukaṇḍakiyā ca nandamātā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘May I be like the laywomen Khujjuttarā and Veḷukaṇṭakī, Nanda’s mother!’"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:133.1.3"
msgid ""
"Esā, bhikkhave, tulā etaṃ pamāṇaṃ mama sāvikānaṃ upāsikānaṃ yadidaṃ "
"khujjuttarā ca upāsikā veḷukaṇḍakiyā ca nandamātā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These are a standard and a measure for my female lay disciples, that is, the "
"laywomen Khujjuttarā and Veḷukaṇṭakī, Nanda’s mother.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.134" id="134"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:133.1.4"
msgid "134"
msgstr "134"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc134.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“When a foolish, incompetent bad person has two qualities they keep "
"themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by "
"sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.1.2"
msgid "Katamehi dvīhi?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.1.3"
msgid "Ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr ""
"Without examining or scrutinizing, they praise those deserving of criticism "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.1.4"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati."
msgstr "and they criticize those deserving of praise."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.1.5"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso "
"khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavatīti."
msgstr ""
"When a foolish, incompetent bad person has these two qualities they keep "
"themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by "
"sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc134.2"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.2.1"
msgid ""
"Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person has two qualities they keep themselves "
"healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by "
"sensible people, and they make much merit."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.2.2"
msgid "Katamehi dvīhi?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.2.3"
msgid "Anuvicca pariyogāhetvā avaṇṇārahassa avaṇṇaṃ bhāsati, "
msgstr ""
"After examining and scrutinizing, they criticize those deserving of "
"criticism "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.2.4"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā vaṇṇārahassa vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati."
msgstr "and they praise those deserving of praise."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.2.5"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso "
"akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca "
"viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person has these two qualities they keep "
"themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much merit.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.135" id="135"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:134.2.6"
msgid "135"
msgstr "135"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc135.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“When a foolish, incompetent bad person has two qualities they keep "
"themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by "
"sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.1.2"
msgid "Katamehi dvīhi?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.1.3"
msgid "Ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti, "
msgstr ""
"Without examining or scrutinizing, they arouse faith in things that are "
"dubious, "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.1.4"
msgid "ananuvicca apariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti."
msgstr "and they don’t arouse faith in things that are inspiring."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.1.5"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato bālo abyatto asappuriso "
"khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavatīti."
msgstr ""
"When a foolish, incompetent bad person has these two qualities they keep "
"themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized by "
"sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.90"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc135.2"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.2.1"
msgid ""
"Dvīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person has two qualities they keep themselves "
"healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized by "
"sensible people, and they make much merit."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.2.2"
msgid "Katamehi dvīhi?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.2.3"
msgid "Anuvicca pariyogāhetvā appasādanīye ṭhāne appasādaṃ upadaṃseti, "
msgstr ""
"After examining or scrutinizing, they don’t arouse faith in things that are "
"dubious, "

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.2.4"
msgid "anuvicca pariyogāhetvā pasādanīye ṭhāne pasādaṃ upadaṃseti."
msgstr "and they do arouse faith in things that are inspiring."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.2.5"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, dvīhi dhammehi samannāgato paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso "
"akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca "
"viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person has these two qualities they keep "
"themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much merit.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.136" id="136"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:135.2.6"
msgid "136"
msgstr "136"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc136.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Dvīsu, bhikkhave, micchāpaṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward two people they "
"keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.1.2"
msgid "Katamesu dvīsu?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.1.3"
msgid "Mātari ca pitari ca."
msgstr "Mother and father."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.1.4"
msgid ""
"Imesu kho, bhikkhave, dvīsu micchāpaṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso "
"khataṃ upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca apuññaṃ pasavatīti."
msgstr ""
"When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward these two people "
"they keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc136.2"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.2.1"
msgid ""
"Dvīsu, bhikkhave, sammāpaṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward two people they "
"keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.2.2"
msgid "Katamesu dvīsu?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.2.3"
msgid "Mātari ca pitari ca."
msgstr "Mother and father."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.2.4"
msgid ""
"Imesu kho, bhikkhave, dvīsu sammāpaṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso "
"akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca "
"viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward these two people "
"they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.137" id="137"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:136.2.5"
msgid "137"
msgstr "137"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc137.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.1.1"
msgid ""
"“Dvīsu, bhikkhave, micchāpaṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"“When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward two people they "
"keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.1.2"
msgid "Katamesu dvīsu?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.1.3"
msgid "Tathāgate ca tathāgatasāvake ca."
msgstr "The Realized One and a disciple of the Realized One."

# Note dvīsu is missing here, it is included in BB.
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.1.4"
msgid ""
"Imesu kho, bhikkhave, micchāpaṭipajjamāno bālo abyatto asappuriso khataṃ "
"upahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, sāvajjo ca hoti sānuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, bahuñca "
"apuññaṃ pasavatīti."
msgstr ""
"When a foolish, incompetent bad person acts wrongly toward these people they "
"keep themselves broken and damaged. They deserve to be blamed and criticized "
"by sensible people, and they make much bad karma."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.91"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc137.2"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.1"
msgid ""
"Dvīsu, bhikkhave, sammāpaṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso akkhataṃ "
"anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca viññūnaṃ, "
"bahuñca puññaṃ pasavati."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward two people they "
"keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.2"
msgid "Katamesu dvīsu?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.3"
msgid "Tathāgate ca tathāgatasāvake ca."
msgstr "The Realized One and a disciple of the Realized One."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.4"
msgid ""
"Imesu kho, bhikkhave, dvīsu sammāpaṭipajjamāno paṇḍito viyatto sappuriso "
"akkhataṃ anupahataṃ attānaṃ pariharati, anavajjo ca hoti ananuvajjo ca "
"viññūnaṃ, bahuñca puññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"When an astute, competent good person acts rightly toward these two people "
"they keep themselves healthy and whole. They don’t deserve to be blamed and "
"criticized by sensible people, and they make much merit.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.138" id="138"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:137.2.5"
msgid "138"
msgstr "138"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc138.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.1"
msgid "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "“There are these two things."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.3"
msgid "Sacittavodānañca na ca kiñci loke upādiyati."
msgstr "Cleaning your own mind, and not grasping at anything in the world."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā”ti."
msgstr "These are the two things.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.139" id="139"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:138.1.5"
msgid "139"
msgstr "139"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc139.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.1"
msgid "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "“There are these two things."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.3"
msgid "Kodho ca upanāho ca."
msgstr "Anger and hostility."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā”ti."
msgstr "These are the two things.”"

#. </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.140" id="140"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:139.1.5"
msgid "140"
msgstr "140"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc140.1"></a>
msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.1"
msgid "“Dveme, bhikkhave, dhammā."
msgstr "“There are these two things."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.2"
msgid "Katame dve?"
msgstr "What two?"

msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.3"
msgid "Kodhavinayo ca upanāhavinayo ca."
msgstr "Dispelling anger and dispelling hostility."

msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, dve dhammā”ti."
msgstr "These are the two things.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an2.130-140:140.1.5"
msgid "Āyācanavaggo dutiyo."
msgstr ""
